com.taobao.datax.engine.schedule
类 PluginWorker

java.lang.Object
  com.taobao.datax.engine.schedule.PluginWorker
直接已知子类：
ReaderWorker, SplitWorker, WriterWorker
public abstract class PluginWorker
extends java.lang.Object

PluginWorker represents executor of Plugin.
DataX Engine uses PluginWorker to load methods from each Plugin by reflections
and call each method later.
